Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:28.83,ThemeSong - JP,,0,0,0,,都合良い理想ばつか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:28.83,ThemeSong - CN,,0,0,0,,僅去面對更有益的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:32.64,ThemeSong - JP,,0,0,0,,並べたって現実は暗い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:32.64,ThemeSong - CN,,0,0,0,,可現實卻是無垠黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:39.01,ThemeSong - JP,,0,0,0,,傷つくのが癖になってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:39.01,ThemeSong - CN,,0,0,0,,早已習慣身心飽受創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:44.31,ThemeSong - JP,,0,0,0,,誰を許せないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:44.31,ThemeSong - CN,,0,0,0,,難道就誰也不能原諒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:47.60,ThemeSong - JP,,0,0,0,,愛したいものから壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:47.60,ThemeSong - CN,,0,0,0,,若是摧毀從所愛之物開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:52.28,ThemeSong - JP,,0,0,0,,失う前に手放してしまえばいいと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:52.28,ThemeSong - CN,,0,0,0,,那麼在失去之前放棄或許更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:55.00,ThemeSong - JP,,0,0,0,,思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:55.00,ThemeSong - CN,,0,0,0,,我這麼想着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:59.11,ThemeSong - JP,,0,0,0,,But I'm crying
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:59.11,ThemeSong - CN,,0,0,0,,But I'm crying
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:23:04.74,ThemeSong - JP,,0,0,0,,今眩しい光の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:23:04.74,ThemeSong - CN,,0,0,0,,現在站在耀眼的燈光下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:10.23,ThemeSong - JP,,0,0,0,,どんな痛みされ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:10.23,ThemeSong - CN,,0,0,0,,無論怎樣的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:14.09,ThemeSong - JP,,0,0,0,,輝きに 変えながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:14.09,ThemeSong - CN,,0,0,0,,都將化作光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:16.80,ThemeSong - JP,,0,0,0,,命を燃やすの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:16.80,ThemeSong - CN,,0,0,0,,燃燒性命
