Dialogue: 8,0:02:01.39,0:02:02.97,Default - CN,,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 8,0:02:02.97,0:02:05.06,Default - CN,,0,0,0,,要換我肯定做不到
Dialogue: 8,0:02:07.13,0:02:10.28,Default - CN,,0,0,0,,所以才會那樣對吧
Dialogue: 8,0:02:10.78,0:02:13.14,Default - CN,,0,0,0,,必須我來說出口對吧
